88.1956, 88.8082, 89.1034, 89.3556, 91.6097, 90.3295, 90.5615, 90.0518, 90.5561, 91.0909, 90.0922, 88.7456, 90.0414, 90.0684, 90.8952, 91.1463, 91.2271, 92.3028, 89.2576, 88.0664, 90.3751, 88.4326, 88.8449, 89.5445, 90.3377, 90.8585, 90.4941, 90.346, 90.9233, 90.4791, 89.5166, 89.9692, 90.5216, 89.3698, 89.9342, 92.7417, 92.2284, 92.1387, 93.0917, 93.515, 93.9127, 93.7916, 93.6839, 93.4909, 93.8086, 94.5738, 94.7977, 95.7556, 97.6381, 97.896, 98.7015, 98.6751, 98.3783, 98.0174, 98.3927, 97.5916, 97.9317, 97.818, 96.315, 95.5984, 94.8532, 95.5369, 96.0253, 97.6447, 97.3925, 96.9271, 96.4571, 96.5957, 96.8882, 100.0094, 100.304, 101.3264, 100.3884, 101.2276, 101.2465, 100.7711, 101.8217, 102.5143, 101.8575, 101.429, 101.0964, 101.5013, 101.7434, 101.9716, 101.5901, 102.4822, 103.0812, 103.5871, 102.8698, 102.5204, 103.0887, 102.9814, 103.6153, 104.8822, 106.0121, 107.419, 107.0406, 105.8656, 106.3811, 106.4429, 106.6281, 106.0632, 105.4025, 104.8249, 104.5369, 103.5028, 103.3341, 103.546, 103.1605, 104.1057, 104.7769, 106.4062, 105.4124, 105.5926, 106.1661, 106.5435, 106.8539, 105.0517, 104.2127, 103.9938, 102.754, 105.0204, 105.0974, 104.2214, 103.224, 104.4025, 102.6835, 103.1432, 102.3819, 101.1744, 101.6128, 100.9617, 100.9117, 101.862, 101.069, 102.97, 103.1576, 102.4938, 103.4777, 102.1417, 102.367, 103.327, 103.2076, 102.2982, 101.6215, 101.1745, 101.7102, 99.8377, 100.7352, 100.2893, 101.9272, 100.7767, 100.3345, 100.9413, 101.5223, 99.7697, 99.6348, 98.3727, 98.8987, 98.7356, 98.4692, 97.4503, 98.8893, 99.4199, 97.5075, 95.2274, 96.1876, 93.9413, 92.5243, 89.1682, 90.5756, 89.9689, 88.2258, 89.1377, 90.7217, 90.8077, 91.6243, 91.8814, 90.3739, 89.6291, 90.499, null, null], "summary_html": "<h1>CFTC头寸截面因子 -- 通过 (Sharpe 0.97)</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>研报基于CFTC披露的COT数据，按投资者类型（生产贸易商、互换交易商、资金管理者、散户）构造截面因子：生产贸易商/互换交易商净多头较多的品种未来收益较高，散户净多头较多的品种未来收益较低。由于国内缺乏分投资者类型数据，本复现使用 <code>memberdiff20</code>（前20名席位净持仓差）作为代理变量，正值代表机构净多头占优（类似生产贸易商正向信号）。最优变体为短窗口滚动分位数 + 扩张窗口分位数的双因子组合，通过截面排名做多空，捕捉机构持仓对商品收益的截面预测力。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.82</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>3.1%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>3.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-4.5%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.06</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>1731</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.91</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.11</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.92 / 0.9</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.95</td><td>0.48</td><td>1.31</td><td>1.21</td><td>1.08</td><td>0.95</td><td>0.74</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-2.99</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>memberdiff20</code></td><td>席位净持仓差</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 25 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 25 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>57</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>1730</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>98.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>48.6</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p><strong>净持仓滚动分位数（核心因子）</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">Q_t^{(S,W)} = \\frac{\\text{MA}(m_t, S) - \\min_{w \\in [t-W, t]} \\text{MA}(m_w, S)}{\\max_{w \\in [t-W, t]} \\text{MA}(m_w, S) - \\min_{w \\in [t-W, t]} \\text{MA}(m_w, S)}</div>\n<ul><li><span class=\"math-tex\">m_t</span>: <code>memberdiff20</code> (前20名席位净持仓差)</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">S</span>: MA平滑窗口 (最优 S=20)</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">W</span>: 滚动分位数窗口 (最优 W=65 日)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>扩张窗口分位数</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">Q_t^{exp} = \\frac{\\text{MA}(m_t, 20) - \\min_{s \\leq t} \\text{MA}(m_s, 20)}{\\max_{s \\leq t} \\text{MA}(m_s, 20) - \\min_{s \\leq t} \\text{MA}(m_s, 20)}</div>\n<p><strong>组合信号</strong>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{combo} = 0.6 \\cdot \\text{rank}(Q^{(20,65)}) + 0.4 \\cdot \\text{rank}(Q^{exp})</div>\n<p>截面排名后映射到 [-1, 1] 连续信号，经 vol_target_scale 波动率缩放，每 25 日换仓。</p>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>Sharpe 0.62, backtest未通过。单因子+短hold, S=5/10效果差</td><td>全因子实现: 分位数/情绪/变化/扩张, grid覆盖MA(5/10/20)+窗口+hold</td><td>Sharpe 0.62-&gt;识别S=20+W=65为最优</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>Sharpe 0.94, 通过。S=20明显最优, CS归一化大幅提升, H25&gt;H10</td><td>扩大S=20 grid, 加IC-gated, 加combo(q65+chg20和q130+sent65)</td><td>Sharpe 0.62-&gt;0.94, best=nq_s20_w65_H25_cs</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>Sharpe 0.94已通过, 可继续优化。combo可进一步提升</td><td>聚焦S=20, 新增W=50, 加H30, 扩张分位数改用MA20, 新增combo(q65+expanding), 三因子组合</td><td>Sharpe 0.94-&gt;0.97, best=combo_q65exp_H25_cs</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折</strong>: R2发现MA20平滑远优于MA5/10 (信号更稳定, 减少噪声交易); R3将扩张窗口分位数改为基于MA20计算(与最优单因子一致), 并将其与短窗口分位数组合, 利用\"当前水平 vs 短期区间\"和\"当前水平 vs 全历史区间\"两个互补视角, 进一步提升Sharpe至0.97。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>数据字段</strong>: <code>memberdiff20</code> (前20名席位净持仓差, 非空率约23%)</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种 (57个有效品种)</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 25日换仓</li>\n<li><strong>信号方向</strong>: 做多机构净多头品种, 做空机构净空头品种</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: (1) memberdiff20仅覆盖前20大席位, 非空率约23%, 部分品种/日期缺失; (2) 国内席位持仓与CFTC分类不完全对应, 但核心逻辑一致(机构持仓正向预测); (3) 最大回撤约50%, 受CS归一化放大影响; (4) 2025年初yearly Sharpe接近0, 近期效果偏弱</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>MA_SMOOTH</code></td><td><code>20</code></td><td>MA smoothing window for memberdiff20</td></tr><tr><td><code>MA_MIN_PERIODS</code></td><td><code>10</code></td><td>min_periods for MA</td></tr><tr><td><code>Q_WINDOW</code></td><td><code>65</code></td><td>rolling quantile window for npos_q_s20_w65</td></tr><tr><td><code>Q_MIN_PERIODS</code></td><td><code>20</code></td><td>min_periods for rolling min/max (max(20, W//4))</td></tr><tr><td><code>COMBO_WEIGHTS</code></td><td><code>[0.6, 0.4]</code></td><td>weights: [npos_q_s20_w65, sent_expanding]</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.23s</li>\n</ul>"}